title: Start
---
Ilya Voss sits three districts away from the gala with PhantomRoot biting into their visual cortex.

The contract is simple on paper: Silas Wren must die before midnight, and the proof packet must show he never saw the hand that killed him.

Vale Nyx is already inside with camera contacts. Juno Kade controls the security spine. The hit is remote, but the consequences are very physical.
===
